        "userConfig" : {
          "system" : "Generate a concise clinical summary of this medical report for physician review. Structure the summary as: (1) Chief Complaint, (2) Key Findings, (3) Assessment, (4) Recommended Follow-up Actions. Keep the summary focused, clinically relevant, and suitable for inclusion in a physician's case notes.",
